Virtual environment is must for this project as there are multiple dependencies in this project.Virtual environment commands are as follows : 
python -m venv venv (creating virtual env in WINDOWS) & venv\Scripts\activate (activating the virtual env in WINDOWS)
python3 -m venv venv (creating virtual env in UBUNTU) & source venv/bin/activate (activating virtual env in UBUNTU)

Choosing interpreter is the second step which can be done by the below command : 
a)Press Ctrl+Shift+P and search for Python: Select Interpreter
b)Choose the interpreter from your venv folder (it will look like .venv/bin/python or venv\Scripts\python.exe).


The below commands are to be executed for the purpose of installing the necessary libraries : 

pip install numpy
pip install joblib
pip install SpeechRecognition
pip install scikit-learn
pip install easyocr
pip install matplotlib
pip install fastapi
pip install python-multipart
pip install PyMuPDF



 

 
